name: Ocular Ego
description: By Travis LeRoy Southworth | @travisleroy | "Ocular Ego" (2021) is a digital painting partly created through a GAN and my own brush strokes in Photoshop.  It is the first work in my series "Thresholds". A 'threshold' can be a boundary or a starting point of an experience.  I like its connection to the words 'thresh,'  meaning "to separate seed from a plant using a machine " and 'thrash,' meaning "to beat soundly or go over again and again."
